(40, 15, 10, 23, 6, 9, 9, 'Hear, and understand', 'Hearing and Understanding', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of hearing and understanding. Matthew calls the multitude to hear and understand, while Isaiah describes a people who hear but do not understand.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
